                              key="place_7008653">Britain</placeName>, with ~19 laid lines per 20
                           mm, 27 mm between chain lines, and average thicknes of 100 microns
                           measured on the first text folios, watermarked with a
                              <watermark>VEIC</watermark> (East India Company) insignia and
